$$\left| {\overrightarrow A  \times \overrightarrow B } \right| = \sqrt 3 \left( {\overrightarrow A .\overrightarrow B } \right)$$<br><br>
$$ \therefore $$ $$AB\sin \theta  = \sqrt 3 AB\cos \theta $$<br><br>
or $$\tan \theta  = \sqrt 3 $$ or $$\theta  = {\tan ^{ - 1}}\sqrt 3  = 60^\circ $$;
